data.description: A spacious 5 bed/3 bath home has incredible curb appeal in sought after Sunset Terrace, close to Downtown, River trail access & straight shot to beautiful Whiskytown lake & hiking. 2 Spacious living rooms, Gourmets will delight in the thoughtfully updated kitchen, newer appliances, butcher block & granite countertops, new lighting & more. Excellent indoor/outdoor flow w/ new french doors leading out to the back deck and yard. The floor plan offers nice separation of space, a bonus room/den downstairs w/ wet bar in addition to 2 more bedrooms & a full bathroom - great for hosting guests, or possibly convert to separate living? Enjoy the beautifully landscaped fenced yard that creates a dreamy backdrop for many memories to come. Make move-in or investment opportunity a breeze... Currently fully furnished. Property has functioned as a successful furnished rental - Comfortably sleeps 14. All furnishings up for negotiation w/ the right offer. Seller credit rate buy down options available.
